# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ecommerce Factory — monorepo root .gitignore
#
# This repository contains ONLY the two applications below. The working
# directory may hold unrelated projects/files; everything is ignored by default
# and only the product is tracked. Each app has its own .gitignore for
# node_modules / .next / env files.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Ignore everything at the repo root by default…
/*

# …then track only the product.
!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes
!/README.md
!/ecommerce-lite/
!/marketing-site/

# Safety: never commit dependencies, build output or local env (covered by the
# per-app .gitignore too, listed here as a backstop).
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/.open-next/
**/.wrangler/
**/out/
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env*.local
**/.data/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts
.DS_Store
